{"tid":21151,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"新垣結衣自爆懶洗澡！現已改邪歸正！","createTime":"2016-12-03T16:40:42.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-04T03:31:12.000Z","uid":20473,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"5754b0c399b22905ea654fb1ab941e8acbaa216b","tid":21151,"uid":20473,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T16:40:42.000Z","msg":"新垣結衣自爆懶洗澡！現已改邪歸正！<br />\n<br />\n在此前有傳新垣結衣曾經在娛樂節目當中坦言自己討厭洗澡。並且一些節目的工作人員也說她每次都是穿著同樣的衣服。由於在日本，每天洗澡、換衣服是很多人的習慣，因此如果總是穿一樣的服裝，就很容易給人不愛乾淨的印象。<br />\n<br />\n不過目前開始痴迷於網絡了，只要不是工作的話，基本上就泡在網上，她本人在網絡上看到了有關不洗澡的人不干淨、總是穿著很老土的衣服這樣的新聞，因此深受打擊。在那之後，她就戒掉了懶散的生活，最近她終於有好好地洗澡了。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://image.gameapps.hk/images/201612/02/DE2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimage.gameapps.hk%2Fimages%2F201612%2F02%2FDE2.jpg&h=a8b2ee37&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"899ea90606e726b8f3d2fd90ce0e43586fbaa9dd","tid":21151,"uid":26156,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T16:51:27.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b15d8742072fb7430d6866ce0067c84b8e1fc5e8","tid":21151,"uid":20473,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T03:02:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ad74c8508ca5b289304106cc66ba78def8064b1","tid":21151,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T03:03:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f44825f18109c1b51e005f0c821e088e10e8e37","tid":21151,"uid":47492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T03:31:12.000Z","msg":"那個了哦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}